data.text:
1. DAVID FERRER

2. information • He is a Spanish tennis player. • He is 32. • At present, he’s the sixth best in the world. And the best in this sport is Novak Djokovic. • Ferrer turned pro in 2000. • A year ago, he was the third best tennis player in the world.

3. BIOGRAPHY • David Ferrer García was born on the second of April, 1982. Now, he’s 32. • He’s from Jávea, Alicante, Spain. • Now, David Ferrer is living in Valencia with his girlfriend and her personal trainer.

4. TRACK RECORD • In total, Ferrer has got 20 trophies. • The best that he has, a Master 1000, is one of the best trophies that you can win in this sport.
